Randompics Dokuwiki Plugin
Doug Burner
2013-06-28

- Unpack in the <wiki_root>/lib/plugins directory.
    $ sudo tar xf randompics.tgz
- Change ownership to apache:apache
    $ sudo chown -R apache:apache randompics

-OR-

- From the plugin manager (Admin - Manage Plugins), enter "https://github.com/doug869/dokuwiki_plugin_randompics/archive/master.zip" in the plugin URL and dowload.

- Point a browser to the Administration - Configuration Settings panel and set 'cachetime' to 60
- Edit a wiki page and add the '[RANDOMPICS]' token.

Thanks to Phil Chadwick for supplying most of the quotes.

